Package com.adobe.cq.social.members.endpoints Description

This package contains interfaces for getting operations available for community users/groups and classes, that implement functionality for community group post operation. The AbstractCommunityMemberGroupProfileOperation class provides functionality to perform post operation and sends the response using the provided session. The AbstractCommunityMemberGroupProfileOperationService class contains implementation of CommunityMemberGroupProfileOperations class. The CommunityMemberGroupProfileOperationExtension class provides functionality for getting operation extensions for community group. The CommunityMemberGroupProfileOperations class provides functionality to perform operations on community groups. The CommunityMemberUserProfileOperationExtension class provides functionality for getting operation extensions for community user. The CommunityMemberUserProfileOperations class provides functionality to perform operations on community users.
